quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,Alm
  32,2,"Tarusi n Tezmamt, ur illi degs ccekk, s$uĂŽ Mass imavalen"
  32,3,"Ne$ a d inin: \"isnulfa p id\". XaĂźi, neppat, d tidep s$uĂŽ Mass ik, iwakken a pnedĂŽev agdud u$uĂŽ ur d iusi ara uneddaĂŽ, uqbel ik, amar ad pwanhun"
  32,4,"Ăebbi i Ixelqen tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan; sinna, IĂąannec $ef usgeld. Ur tesĂąim, war Neppa, bab, ne$ amcafaĂą. Day ula d tesmektayem ara"
  32,5,"A d Iseyyi lameĂŽ seg igenni ar tmurt; sinna, ad iu$al $uĂŽeS deg ibwass, lmudda s: agim iseggwasen, s leĂȘsab nnwen"
  32,6,"Akka, Umusnaw n wayen iffren, u n wayen ur neffir, Uzmir IpĂȘunun"
  32,7,"I IĂ»Ă»egmen akw ayen Ixleq. Inza d lxelq n umdan, si talaxt"
  32,8,"Sinna, Issuffe$ ed tarwa s si l$ella, degs cwiĂź n waman"
  32,9,"Sinna, Imesl it, IĂ»Ă»uv degs, si ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ iS. Irra yawen timesliwt, iĂ©ĂŽi, ul. Drus ay tesnemmirem"
  32,10,"Nnan: \"ma nweddeĂŽ di tmurt, day a d nepwaxleq tikelt nniven\"? XaĂźi, nekĂŽen timlilit akked Mass nnsen"
  32,11,"Ini: \"ad iddem ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ nnwen, lmelk n tmeppant i ippukelfen fellawen. Sinna, ar Mass nnwen a ppu$alem"
  32,12,"Lemmer a pwaliv ibe$wviyen, ad brun i iqweĂŽĂŽa nnsen, zdat Mass nnsen: \"a Mass nne$! Nwala, nesla; Err ane$ a nexdem ayen ilhan. S tidep, numen"
  32,13,"Lemmer i ÂŁ ihwi, yili Nefka, i yal ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ, nnhaya s. Maca, ad ivĂŽu wayen Nni$: \"war ccekk, ad AcaĂŽe$ Loahennama s leonun akked yimdanen, mejmulen"
  32,14,"Ihi, jeĂŽĂŽbet imi teppum a d temlilem d wass nnwen agi! Nekwni, ih, Neppu kwen. JeĂŽĂŽbet aĂąaqeb, n lebda, ilmend n wayen txeddmem"
  32,15,"I iumnen kan, s issekniyen nneÂŁ, d wid, mara ten id mmektin, ara weddin ad knun, ara isbucuĂąen Mass nnsen s ccekĂŽan, nitni ur pzuxxun"
  32,16,"Ppensaren d ibeĂŽdiyen nnsen, seg imĂźeĂŽĂȘen, pnujun $eĂŽ Mass nnsen, s tugwdi d usirem. Seg wayen iten N$at, pseddiqen"
  32,17,Ur iĂ©ĂŽi yiwen acu i sen Ffre$ n lfeĂŽĂȘ. D arraz n wayen llan xeddmen
  32,18,"Win illan d lmumen, day am win illan d amed$ul? Ur aĂądilen"
  32,19,"Ihi, i wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, leonanat imĂŽaĂȘbiyen, ara zed$en, ilmend n wayen xeddmeĂčn"
  32,20,"Wanag wid ide$wlen, di tmes ara zed$en. Yal tikelt ideg ara b$un a d ff$en segs, a ten rren $uĂŽes, ad asen inin: \"jeĂŽĂŽbet aĂąaqeb n tmes i tnekkĂŽem"
  32,21,"Ih, a Nessukk fellasen aĂąaqeb aqĂŽib mavi, war aĂąaqeb abarar. Ahat a d u$alen s abrid"
  32,22,"Anwa i idensen sennig n win iwumi d dekĂŽen issekniyen n Mass is, iu$al iwexxeĂŽ asen? Ih, a d Nerr ppaĂŽ seg ibe$wviyen"
  32,23,Ni$ Nefka yas Tazmamt i Musa. Ur ppili di ccekk af temlilit yideS! Nerra p d nnhaya i At IsĂŽail
  32,24,"Nesbedd, segsen, iselmaden; nnehun s lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, mi Ă»ebĂŽen, u llan pputebbten $ef issekniyen nneÂŁ"
  32,25,"Ih, Mass ik, Neppa, ad IĂȘudd garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen i$ef mgarraden"
  32,26,"Day ur ten inha ara wayen Nesqucc isuta, uqbel nnsen? La leĂȘĂȘun $ef tnezdu$in nnsen. Deg waya, s tidep, issekniyen. Day ur sellen ara"
  32,27,"Day ur zĂŽin ara Neppawi aman s akal aquĂŽan; Nessuffu$ ed, yissen, iĂąaqqayen; teppen, segsen, nitni akked lmal nnsen. Day ur pwalin ara"
  32,28,"QqaĂŽen: \"melmi l$elb agi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  32,29,"Ini: \"ass n l$elb, liman n wid ijehlen, ur ten infaĂą; ur pganin"
  32,30,"Ihi, wexxeĂŽ asen, ggani. Nitni, s tidep, la pganin"